gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T16:35:06.000Z","msg":"Trump to boy: Do you believe in Santa?<br />\n<br />\n咁樣可以translate到 你還相信聖誕老人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n華文傳媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f51aa9ee8792ae92a81c72ca55bfd96db94045a","tid":955371,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f15ff000a5a7825d8b88e7c2730e59579e6a20c3","tid":955371,"uid":135274,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T12:02:30.000Z","msg":"其實係防空司令部有接聽小朋友電話報導聖誕老人行蹤既傳統，所以Trump俾人感覺最大問題係破壞咗呢個傳統<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T16:42:47.000Z","msg":"一向總統或佢老婆都會接電話的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<ul><br />\n&bull;'Are you still a believer in Santa?' President Trump asked a caller to the Santa Tracker. 'Because at seven it's marginal, right?'<br />\n&bull;Melania Trump makes it back from Florida in time to join her husband in the holiday tradition of taking phone calls from children hoping to track Santa Claus on Christmas Eve  <br />\n&bull;She flew back during the day as the President spent it tweeting about 'poor me' all alone in the White House<br />\n&bull;President Trump has been mired in crises from a partial government shutdown to a stock market selloff amid his public criticisms of the Federal Reserve<br />\n</ul> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/25/02/7802504-6528017-image-a-46_1545704405226.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F25%2F02%2F7802504-6528017-image-a-46_1545704405226.jpg&h=4b22af38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 'Are you still a believer in Santa?' President Trump asked a young caller. 'Because at seven it's marginal, right?'<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/25/02/7802484-0-image-a-47_1545704423291.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F25%2F02%2F7802484-0-image-a-47_1545704423291.jpg&h=1df7d50e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Melania Trump flew back from Florida today to be with the president as they surprised children calling the NORAD Santa Tracker hotline <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/25/02/7802520-6528017-image-a-49_1545704439376.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F25%2F02%2F7802520-6528017-image-a-49_1545704439376.jpg&h=c0d798a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n First lady Melania Trump joined the president and told a caller Santa was in the Sahara.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/25/14/7802482-6528017-First_lady_Melania_Trump_left_and_President_Trump_right_took_cal-a-3_1545747393233.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F25%2F14%2F7802482-6528017-First_lady_Melania_Trump_left_and_President_Trump_right_took_cal-a-3_1545747393233.jpg&h=90f5fc24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n First lady Melania  Trump (left) and President Trump (right) took calls from children tracking Santa this year from the White House<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/25/06/7802980-6528017-The_first_lady_tweeted_about_her_enjoyment_of_the_tradition_of_t-a-2_1545720472202.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F25%2F06%2F7802980-6528017-The_first_lady_tweeted_about_her_enjoyment_of_the_tradition_of_t-a-2_1545720472202.jpg&h=92769708&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The first lady tweeted about her enjoyment of the tradition of talking to kids hoping to keep a track of Santa Claus<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/25/06/7802496-6528017-At_one_point_Melania_reported_that_Santa_was_far_away_in_Morocco-a-3_1545720472228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F25%2F06%2F7802496-6528017-At_one_point_Melania_reported_that_Santa_was_far_away_in_Morocco-a-3_1545720472228.jpg&h=f6b7aa3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n At one point Melania reported that Santa was far away in Morocco but would be at the caller's home on Christmas morning<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/12/25/6384540032747683313/1024x576_MP4_6384540032747683313.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideos.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2018%2F12%2F25%2F6384540032747683313%2F1024x576_MP4_6384540032747683313.mp4&d=9C3NZCD0Ec3bYwCro%2B3203Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=25e64786\" target=\"_blank\">https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/12/25/6384540032747683313/1024x576_MP4_6384540032747683313.mp4</a><br />\n Trump and Melania take Christmas calls from children<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/12/24/7836552074367580928/1024x576_MP4_7836552074367580928.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideos.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2018%2F12%2F24%2F7836552074367580928%2F1024x576_MP4_7836552074367580928.mp4&d=9C3NZCD0Ec3bYwCro%2B3203Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=dd30a99e\" target=\"_blank\">https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/12/24/7836552074367580928/1024x576_MP4_7836552074367580928.mp4</a><br />\n NORAD tracks Santa's progress as he delivers gifts around the world<br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6528017/Melania-reunites-Trump-surprise-kids-calling-NORADs-Santa-tracker-left-alone.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-6528017%2FMelania-reunites-Trump-surprise-kids-calling-NORADs-Santa-tracker-left-alone.html&d=9C3NZCD0Ec3bYwCro%2B3203Iou9i